{
  "text": "We found no evidence that a longer period prior to accessing treatment was associated with more severe illness at presentation in terms of global symptom levels. Although an association between longer DUP and higher global symptom ratings has been reported, [CITATION_1] our finding utilising a DUI measure is in line with the consensus using DUP.",
